## Key Files
- [COMPREHENSIVE_EVALUATION.md](mdc:COMPREHENSIVE_EVALUATION.md) - Complete project evaluation
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project overview
- Each module contains:
  - `cppXX/` - Assignment requirements (images)
  - `ng_4_cpp_module_XX/` - Evaluation criteria
  - `ex00/`, `ex01/`, etc. - Exercise implementations

## Exercise Structure
Each exercise directory contains:
- `Makefile` - Build configuration
- `*.hpp` - Header files (class declarations)
- `*.cpp` - Source files (class implementations)
- `main.cpp` - Test/demo program
- Executable (after compilation)

